name: Tanya_Mane
content: Tanya Mane, known by her nicknamed Tanya "Trickshot" Mane, was a dark-skinned Human female smuggler active during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire. She made frequent stops to the planet Taris before the Imperial invasion of the world, and could be found in the city of Olaris where she shared her knowledge with other smugglers.
